name: DOOMBIT 2000
description:
Classic Creature #4

DOOMBIT 2000 was fabricated in the year 2000, but a different year 2000. The year 2000 imagined in the year 1900, when paranoid sci-fi writers came together in a Black Mass and harnessed so much sci-fi energy they created a spin-off dimension where DOOMBIT 2000 was built to destroy and dominate and data-crunch. 

Created in VR, Finished in 3D.
